.TH "STYLESHEET.MEDIA" "3JS" "November 25, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
StyleSheet.media \- StyleSheet: media property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The read\-only \f[B]\f[CB]media\f[B]\f[R] property of the
\f[CR]StyleSheet\f[R] interface contains a \f[CR]MediaList\f[R] object
representing the intended destination media for style information.
.SH VALUE
A \f[CR]MediaList\f[R] object.
Its value is set by the \f[CR]media\f[R] attribute on the corresponding
\f[CR]<link>\f[R] or \f[CR]<style>\f[R] element.
If the \f[CR]media\f[R] attribute is not set or empty, it returns an
empty \f[CR]MediaList\f[R], i.e., a \f[CR]MediaList\f[R] with the
\f[CR]length\f[R] property equal to \f[CR]0\f[R].
.PP
Although the \f[CR]media\f[R] property itself is read\-only in the sense
that you can\(cqt replace the \f[CR]MediaList\f[R] object, you can still
assign to the \f[CR]media\f[R] property directly, which is equivalent to
assigning to its \f[CR]mediaText\f[R] property.
You can also modify the \f[CR]MediaList\f[R] object using the
\f[CR]appendMedium()\f[R] and \f[CR]deleteMedium()\f[R] methods.
.SH EXAMPLES
Assume the \f[CR]<head>\f[R] contains the following:
.IP
.EX
<\f[B]link\f[R] rel=\(dqstylesheet\(dq href=\(dqdocument.css\(dq media=\(dqscreen\(dq />
<\f[B]style\f[R] rel=\(dqstylesheet\(dq media=\(dqscreen, print\(dq>
  body {
    \f[B]background\-color\f[R]: snow;
  }
</\f[B]style\f[R]>
.EE
.PP
Then:
.IP
.EX
\f[B]for\f[R] (\f[B]let\f[R] i = 0; i < document.styleSheets.length; i++) {
  console.log(
    \(gadocument.styleSheets[${i}].media: ${JSON.stringify(
      document.styleSheets[i].media,
    )}\(ga,
  );
  \f[B]if\f[R] (i === 0) document.styleSheets[i].media.appendMedium(\(dqhandheld\(dq);
  \f[B]if\f[R] (i === 1) document.styleSheets[i].media.deleteMedium(\(dqprint\(dq);
  console.log(
    \(gadocument.styleSheets[${i}].media: ${JSON.stringify(
      document.styleSheets[i].media,
    )}\(ga,
  );
}
\f[I]// This will log:\f[R]
\f[I]// document.styleSheets[0].media: {\(dq0\(dq:\(dqscreen\(dq}\f[R]
\f[I]// document.styleSheets[0].media: {\(dq0\(dq:\(dqscreen\(dq,\(dq1\(dq:\(dqhandheld\(dq}\f[R]
\f[I]// document.styleSheets[1].media: {\(dq0\(dq:\(dqscreen\(dq,\(dq1\(dq:\(dqprint\(dq}\f[R]
\f[I]// document.styleSheets[1].media: {\(dq0\(dq:\(dqscreen\(dq}\f[R]
.EE
